\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "FisherShell1968"
literal "false"

\end_inset

for the classical approach to the problem).
 Thus we observe how the cost of a standard basket of basic needs varies
 across the regions and districts in the economy and infer the varying cost
